webpackJsonp([0xfeb3658c1040],{4930:function(t,e){t.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Christmas Market Monday",date:"03 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-03-christmas-market-monday/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p>J decided that <a href="http://www.jbittner.com/germany/2006/12/4-december-2006-is-christmas-market.html">tomorrow would be Christmas Market Monday</a>, when we all post pictures from our visits to our local Christmas Markets this past weekend. I usually don\'t go along with special blogging days, but since we were meeting Oma at the Christmas Market in Buchholz anyway, I brought my camera along. Just to be a non-conformist, I\'m posting mine a day early. There\'s a <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/papascott/sets/72157594403825079/detail7">set at flickr</a>, and a slideshow <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/papascott/sets/72157594403825079/show/">here</a>. I tried to tell a story with the captions, so maybe the <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/papascott/sets/72157594403825079/detail/">plain view</a> is better than the slideshow (where you have to click on each picture to see the caption).</p>\n<p><a href="http://flickr.com/photos/papascott/sets/72157594403825079/detail/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://static.flickr.com/116/313145816_1459e156c7.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG 1827" /></a></p>\n<p>It would have been funnier to go to the <a href="http://www.hamburg.de/event.do?cid=6513353">"Santa Pauli" Christmas Market</a> on Spielbudenplatz, which features booths from FC St. Pauli and a various sex shops, since we were in the area on Friday. Actually not, since it was so blatantly commercial and was most definately inappropriate for children. We didn\'t stop.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"No Accident",date:"02 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-02-no-accident/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Do-It-Yourself Advent Calendar",date:"03 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-03-do-it-yourself-advent-calendar/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"No Accident",date:"02 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-02-no-accident/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p>Headline from Spiegel Online:</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n  <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/panorama/0,1518,452163,00.html">Accident at Reptile Show</a>: Crocodile Snaps, Circus Director Loses Thumb\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>Somehow that doesn\'t sound accidental.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Jim Knopf and Christopher",date:"02 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-02-jim-knopf-and-christopher/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Christmas Market Monday",date:"03 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-03-christmas-market-monday/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Jim Knopf and Christopher",date:"02 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-02-jim-knopf-and-christopher/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/311920609/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://static.flickr.com/105/311920609_d52e96b258_o.jpg" width="500" height="406" alt="jimknopf" /></a></p>\n<p>We went to see the musical version of <a href="http://tivoli.de/index.php?id=event843">Jim Knopf und Lukas der Lokomotivfuhrer</a> at the Schmidt Theatre in Hamburg yesterday. As you can see, Christopher was very happy to have his picture (a scan of a polaroid) taken with the star. We can highly recommend it.</p>\n<p>As a bonus, here\'s the annual Christmas Cookie Cutter picture.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/311931666/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://static.flickr.com/116/311931666_6999e98b23.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG 1815" /></a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Major Medical Breakthrough",date:"01 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-01-major-medical-breakthrough/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"No Accident",date:"02 Dec 2006",slug:"/2006-12-02-no-accident/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:174,pageCount:1101}}}});
